3.title: Under the Microscope

episode of.title: Couples Therapy with Dr. Jenn (TV Series 2014– )

3.plot: Group therapy brings up many topics revolving around trust in a time when social media is so prevalent in society. Each couple has issues with trust, especially Juan Pablo and Nikki, and Treach and Cicely, who all get into disagreements about how to approach their relationships with fans, and with each other. After group, Treach and Cicely get into a heated argument about her not believing if Treach has been faithful to Cicely.

4.title: Called Out

episode of.title: Couples Therapy with Dr. Jenn (TV Series 2014– )

4.plot: Dr. Jenn is upset with both Nikki and Jenna for not fully committing to the process, so she brings everybody into a group session to scold the pair. Nikki takes what Dr. Jenn says to heart, but it does the opposite for Jenna, who is furious with Dr. Jenn. Jenna then confronts Dr. Jenn about what she had said to her, and even though Dr. Jenn apologizes, Jenna is still shaken and trigged. The group realizes that Dr. Jenn was right: Nikki can be cagey, secretive, overly opinionated and outspoken.

5.title: The Truth Is Out There

episode of.title: Couples Therapy with Dr. Jenn (TV Series 2014– )

5.plot: Dr. Jenn shakes things up with the group by bringing in a trust expert to the house. Cicely takes advantage of the situation by calling Treach out about her thinking he has cheated on her in the past, Stephanie reveals if there is any chance she will get back together with Evel, and Juan Pablo reveals whether or not he loves Nikki. All of this sends the couples spinning in their relationships, each feeling burned and upset by their partner.

6.title: I've Got the Power

episode of.title: Couples Therapy with Dr. Jenn (TV Series 2014– )

6.plot: Evel admits to the cast that he has a life threatening disease, and the cast has a very surprising response. Treach and Cicely are still fuming mad with each other, and haven't spoken since she called him out at the trust exercise. Nikki is still reeling over Juan Pablo not telling her he loves her, and the rest of the group is getting sick of hearing the same thing over and over again from her.

7.title: Reflections of the Past

episode of.title: Couples Therapy with Dr. Jenn (TV Series 2014– )

7.plot: Dr. Jenn opens this weeks group session with a heartbreaking topic: childhood trauma. Later, Dr. Jenn plans an activity allowing the couples to release their aggression. Nikki and Juan Pablo get into a huge argument that ends up involving everyone in the house.

9.title: Meatball Problems

episode of.title: Couples Therapy with Dr. Jenn (TV Series 2014– )

9.plot: Dr. Jenn opens group therapy with the topic of 'what you need from your partner' and Dick reveals that he is sad and disappointed that he and Stephanie have parted ways, but he needs to have her in his life leaving therapy.

10.title: Fighting 'Till the End

episode of.title: Couples Therapy with Dr. Jenn (TV Series 2014– )

10.plot: After 3 long weeks in therapy, the couples are gearing up to leave the retreat, but Dr. Jenn still has her hands full. Dr. Jenn has planned a very special final dinner for the group on a boat in the marina, and everybody is excited, except Treach and Cicely, who are on the brink of breaking up.
